<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1626,1975]" pageId="1" pageNumber="467">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,239,1626,1651]" pageId="1" pageNumber="467">Biology</emphasis>
. Mature larvae had fecal material and cast exuviae of previous instars piled on the supra-anal processes. The pupa was attached by its sternum to the leaf surface.
</paragraph>
